summary: Gives Ysolda and Sapphire a makeover without using an esp
descriptionHtml:
[font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]I changed Ysolda's and Sapphire's faces and hairs using nifskope instead of the CK, so no plugin is necessary. It's a common misconception that a plugin is needed. It can be needed depending on what you are doing, but if only doing things like this it is not

Created with vanilla skin or UNP skin in mind

Takes a bit of time to customize each one this way, so just two right now for demonstration. Probably parking this and do other things, just thought I'd throw the concept out there

Credits:
KS Hairdos which I borrowed hair shapes from and Pretty Face for skin textures[/size][/font]
author: Self
